description:
Rustlers On Horseback!

From every corner of the vast territory they came -- the toughest, most ruthless killers in the West! And they all were heading for the Reynolds Ranch! What bloody scheme was being hatched in those brooding hills? When fighting Marshal Rocky Lane buckled on his six-guns and set out to solve this ominous mystery he expected a heap of trouble, but he never dreamed that fate was planning to make him an enemy of the law as the deadliest gun-slinger in the ranks of the Rustlers On Horseback!
name: Rustlers On Horseback!
